name: complex_arith_difference_of_sums_regroups
section: arithmetic-normalization
args: a:Int b:Int c:Int d:Int
type: Bool
expect: True
description: The difference of two sums should regroup to sum the pairwise differences.
law: (= (fuzz-sub (fuzz-add {a} {b}) (fuzz-add {c} {d})) (fuzz-add (fuzz-sub {a} {c}) (fuzz-sub {b} {d})))
